{"word":"G3908 - παρατίθημι - paratíthēmi - par-at-ith'-ay-mee - Allege","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρατίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paratíthēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-at-ith'-ay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Allege</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்வை, பரிமாறு, ஒப்புவி, திருஷ்டாந்தப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to place beside, place near"},{"paragraph":"2. to place down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>place alongside</i>, that is, <i>present</i> (food, truth); by implication to <i>deposit</i> (as a trust or for protection): - allege, commend, commit (the keeping of), put forth, set before.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G114/114\">G114</a>, <a href=\"#/G115/115\">G115</a>, <a href=\"#/G1936/1936\">G1936</a>, <a href=\"#/G2007/2007\">G2007</a>, <a href=\"#/G3331/3331\">G3331</a>, <a href=\"#/G3346/3346\">G3346</a>, <a href=\"#/G3866/3866\">G3866</a>, <a href=\"#/G3908/3908\">G3908</a>, <a href=\"#/G4286/4286\">G4286</a>, <a href=\"#/G4369/4369\">G4369</a>, <a href=\"#/G4388/4388\">G4388</a>, <a href=\"#/G5087/5087\">G5087</a>"}]}